results.title: Slow Cooker Apple Pork Tenderloin
results.summary: You can never have too many main course recipes, so give Slow Cooker Apple Pork Tenderloin a try. This recipe serves 1 and costs $4.41 per serving. One portion of this dish contains around 34g of protein, 7g of fat, and a total of 462 calories. Head to the store and pick up apples, beef broth, pork tenderloin, and a few other things to make it today. This recipe from Pink When has 1 fans. From preparation to the plate, this recipe takes about 45 minutes. It is a good option if you're following a gluten free and dairy free diet. Overall, this recipe earns a solid spoonacular score of 57%. Users who liked this recipe also liked Slow Cooker Apple Pork Tenderloin, Slow Cooker Pork Tenderloin, and Amazing Pork Tenderloin in the Slow Cooker.
